As for import, which is assumed to be the export of goods from a country, it is calculated at the prices of the FOB, or the franc-border of the exporter's country. Thus, international transports across the oceans, air transport, these costs are included in the price of the import goods.

00:24:13.000 --> 00:24:26.000
Only at the time of the crossings of the national economic border, the costs associated with the production and transportation of imports are fully calculated.

