04:31:53.000 --> 04:32:10.000
The financial elements of the system are international financial markets. When we talk about the financial market, it is assumed that this is not only a currency market, but also a fund market, that is, a market of securities and a credit market.

04:32:10.000 --> 04:32:23.000
Accordingly, the financial elements of the system in the form of financial markets can be represented in the interbank market, where the banks are agents and counteragents of this system.

04:32:40.000 --> 04:33:01.000
The second component of the financial elements of the system is the mechanisms of trading specific financial instruments, namely, currencies, securities, loans.

04:33:02.000 --> 04:33:16.000
Financial agents, namely, the currency, fund, and credit markets are represented in the present conditions by individuals, corporations, and the central bank.

04:33:16.000 --> 04:33:31.000
