04:57:03.000 --> 04:57:20.000
This means that the trust in the Russian economy is growing, foreign investors agree to take risks, hope for a reduction in the risk of the national economy, and there are flows of capital to the account of capital.

04:57:20.000 --> 04:57:36.000
The dynamics of export and import of the Russian Federation, as seen from the schemes presented on the slide, also make us proud of the export-import relations of the Russian economy.

04:57:36.000 --> 04:57:56.000
The balance of foreign trade, the difference between export and import, which is marked by the column diagram, is constantly positive, which makes it possible for foreign currencies to flow into the territory of Russia.

04:57:56.000 --> 04:58:13.000
This gives the opportunity to gradually move to full convertibility of the Russian ruble, not only in export-import operations, but also in capital flows.

