Another feature of convertibility is internal and external convertibility. Traditionally, the first step in the process of stabilizing the national currency is the development of measures for internal convertibility.

04:58:38.000 --> 04:59:07.000
This is the right of residents to buy, own and operate within the country with foreign currency assets. Otherwise, it is assumed that if internal convertibility is introduced, then our buyers can exchange dollars for euros, rubles for euros or dollars, and pay their transactions, buy goods for foreign currency, that is, for dollars or euros.

04:59:07.000 --> 04:59:22.000
