The central bank is trying to change the situation on the currency exchange. And then the process is stabilized during the first quarter of 2006. This is due to the fact that at this time, depending on the financial situation, companies are throwing out currency in the form of payments to the market.

05:31:44.000 --> 05:31:56.000
