05:35:37.000 --> 05:36:03.000
And again, the balance will return to 5 rubles per dollar, according to our example. If the situation is 4 rubles per dollar, then at such a low price, of course, they will want to offer the dollar to a smaller number of counteragents, but they will want to buy the dollar to a larger number of agents.

05:36:03.000 --> 05:36:13.000
