05:38:56.000 --> 05:39:11.000
The main policy of the country, which can support the currency rate and stabilize the internal economic system, will be the budgetary-tax policy.

05:39:11.000 --> 05:39:31.000
Of course, transitional economies prefer not a rigidly fixed currency rate, but a currency corridor. But again, any currency rate system that assumes floating allows dishonest players or currency speculators to enter the market.

05:39:31.000 --> 05:39:51.000
And if such an intervention is beneficial to the world community, then the floating currency rate, as well as the regulated floating, is at greater risk than the fixed currency rate.

05:39:51.000 --> 05:40:06.000
