05:50:43.000 --> 05:50:54.000
The price of the carrot has not changed. And now, in order to buy a kilogram of carrots, a foreign importer will pay only 84 cents.

05:50:54.000 --> 05:51:13.000
It turns out that with relatively stable world prices and domestic prices for this product, the relative price in the dollar or foreign currency has decreased, and, accordingly, such an export will be better bought.

05:51:13.000 --> 05:51:38.000
What else is the situation related to the profits from the decrease in the currency exchange rate, in addition to the decrease in prices, which is connected with the Russian situation, which is now subject to the Dutch disease.

