05:55:22.000 --> 05:55:47.000
The level of income that is expressed in the GDP, or in general in the GDP that is created in the country, how it affects the currency exchange rate. It is enough to say that it is good to have rich neighbors. Why? Because they are ready to buy our export at a higher price. Accordingly, the level of income abroad is interesting for our exporters.

